                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871212-15-defend201 t17871212-15-punish92"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
